name: io.bytes.per.checksum
description:
The number of bytes per checksum.  Must not be larger than
  io.file.buffer.size.

name: hadoop.http.authentication.token.validity
description:
Indicates how long (in seconds) an authentication token is valid before it has
    to be renewed.

name: fs.getspaceused.jitterMillis
description: fs space usage statistics refresh jitter in msec.

name: nfs.mountd.port
description: Specify the port number used by Hadoop mount daemon.

name: dfs.namenode.quota.init-threads
description:
The number of concurrent threads to be used in quota initialization. The
    speed of quota initialization also affects the namenode fail-over latency.
    If the size of name space is big, try increasing this to 16 or higher.

name: fs.s3a.committer.threads
description:
Number of threads in committers for parallel operations on files
    (upload, commit, abort, delete...)
